Edition:
Quote:  HALFBEAK (a) Scientific name: <i>Reporhamphus ihi</i>. (b) Suggested commercial name[s]: Garfish; Piper. (c) Other common names: None known. (d) Principal localities where taken: North Auckland, Auckland and Cook Strait.
